  An attempt to make something better than ack, which itself is better than grep.

checksums           rmd160  74d35420e64f19d773d94b0482e18db3ff803339 \
                    sha256  4a42dcb1a265c4923cb0d66ba3b156c19e6770914d7ccf96ad852206df282937

